-- Tesco’s Neville-Rolfe Prepares to Step Down, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 2011-12-18T08:55:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-18/tesco-s-neville-rolfe-prepares-to-step-down-sunday-times-says.html
Lucy Neville-Rolfe, a  director  at
 Tesco Plc (TSCO) , is preparing to step down late next year after 14
years with Britain’s largest supermarket chain, the Sunday Times
 reported , citing unidentified people familiar with the
situation.  The role of Neville-Rolfe, Tesco’s corporate and legal
affairs director, will be split in two, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
 m.carr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  